- Update to version 24.3.3 - changes since 24.1.5 (related: jira#PED-10348)
  * Added VVC decode API
  * Enhanced DPB management for AV1 decoding
  * Supported dynamic resolution change for HEVC/AVC/AV1 decoding in
    VPL memory 2.0
